    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>meat free patty[ies]</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and season with a generous grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Using clean hands, give everything a very good mix up until fully combined</p><p>Divide the mixture into 1 thin patty per person – this are your <strong>chipotle veggie patty[ies]</strong></p>",
